title: 3 Br Condo Lake Stevens
posting_body: ['This is a 3 Bd 2 Bth condo located on the 2nd story, in Lake Stevens, WA.', ' Located in the heart of Frontier Village, and in walking/biking distance to shopping and dining with easy access to I-5.', 'Frontier Village Shopping Center includes a Safeway grocery store, Ross Dress for Less, Ulta, TJ Maxx and Michaels.', ' Target is also close by.', ' Lake Stevens is located 6 miles east of Everett and borders the cities of Marysville to the northwest and Snohomish to the south.', 'The beautiful Lake Stevens is also near by which includes a nice park and boat launch.', 'Amenities include:', 'Living Room w/ Vaulted Ceiling', 'Fireplace', 'Newer Appliances', 'Full Size Front Load Washer & Dryer', '3 Bd 2 Bth', 'Master Bedroom w/ Walk in Closet', 'Master Bathroom w/ Double Sinks', '1 Covered Parking Spot', '1 Single Car Garage - Detached', 'Sewer/Water and Garbage Included', 'No Pets', 'No Smoking', '9 Month Lease - Then Month to Month', '$2500 Security Deposit', 'Available beginning August 15th.', ' Appointments can be scheduled for viewing after review of terms.']
